OL,3,CTom Cruise awarded US Navy honour for
OL,4,Chis role in Top Gun
OL,6,FTom Cruise has landed another medal to
OL,7,Fadd to his trophy cabinet - this time,
OL,8,Ffrom the US Navy.
OL,10,FThe Hollywood actor was awarded the US
OL,11,FNavy's top civilian honour for his
OL,12,F"outstanding contributions" to the
OL,13,Fservice through his role as Lieutenant
OL,14,FPete "Maverick" Mitchell in the film
OL,15,FTop Gun.
OL,17,FUS Navy Secretary Carlos Del Toro, who
OL,18,Fgave him the award, said Cruise's role
OL,19,Fin the 1986 action film "significantly
OL,20,Fincreased" the force's recruitment
OL,21,Fnumbers.
