OL,3,CTom Cruise awarded US Navy honour for
OL,4,Chis role in Top Gun
OL,6,FThe movie features Cruise as a young
OL,7,Fnaval aviator who trains at the US
OL,8,FNavy's fighter weapons school, known
OL,9,Fas Top Gun. The blockbuster drove a
OL,10,Fspike in military enlistment, with the
OL,11,Fnavy even setting up recruitment
OL,12,Ftables in some theatres.
OL,14,FCruise was presented with the
OL,15,FDistinguished Public Service award,
OL,16,Fwhich is given to civilians for acts
OL,17,Fof heroism or support for the navy, on
OL,18,FTuesday at the Longcross Film Studios
OL,19,Fin Surrey.
