OL,3,CTom Cruise awarded US Navy honour for
OL,4,Chis role in Top Gun
OL,6,FMr Del Toro told the audience of
OL,7,FHollywood professionals and US navy
OL,8,Fstaff that Cruise had spent nearly
OL,9,Ffour decades "as an unwavering
OL,10,Fsupporter of the men, women and
OL,11,Ffamilies of the navy marine corps".
OL,13,F"His dedicated support to sailors,
OL,14,Fmarines and civilians through his
OL,15,Fefforts in the film industry increased
OL,16,Fpublic awareness and appreciation for
OL,17,Four highly trained personnel and the
OL,18,Fsacrifices they make while in
OL,19,Funiform," he added.
