OL,3,CTom Cruise awarded US Navy honour for
OL,4,Chis role in Top Gun
OL,6,FAccepting the honour, Cruise told the
OL,7,Faudience: "In life, something that is
OL,8,Fvery true to me is, to lead is to
OL,9,Fserve.
OL,11,F"I know that to my core and I see that
OL,12,Fin the servicemen and women. I
OL,13,Fappreciate everyone's dedication and
OL,14,Fit's a true honour to represent them."
OL,16,FHe said he was "proud and overwhelmed"
OL,17,Fto receive the "extraordinary
OL,18,Facknowledgement."
